WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:03.269
Good morning, family. How are you

00:00:03.269 --> 00:00:03.279
all

00:00:03.279 --> 00:00:06.150
doing? I have a hard word to give

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:11.030
today, and I ask you to be patient

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:14.470
with me here.

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:17.590
You know, as a

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:20.950
prophet, you see things in the future. Refiner's Fire, you

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:23.710
know? And

00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:26.509
I want to say this to

00:00:26.519 --> 00:00:32.869
you all: I take this very

00:00:32.869 --> 00:00:32.879
seriously,

00:00:32.879 --> 00:00:35.030
and the pressure and the

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:38.030
weight of it is a

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:42.110
lot whenever the Lord visits you like He

00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:46.430
does. When Jesus comes and visits you and

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:48.389
you go through that Refiner's Fire that

00:00:48.399 --> 00:00:50.389
I've always talked to you all

00:00:50.399 --> 00:00:53.430
about,

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:56.349
it changes

00:00:56.359 --> 00:01:00.229
you. In that process of that

00:01:00.239 --> 00:01:02.549
Refiner's Fire, you lose yourself and

00:01:02.559 --> 00:01:04.310
everything else around you doesn't

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.590
really matter

00:01:06.590 --> 00:01:06.600
anymore—money,

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:11.670
fame,

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:14.950
whatever. I do it all for

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:17.270
Him. The whole

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:20.149
thing is out of

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:24.390
compassion and love for

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:28.030
Jesus; nothing else matters to

00:01:28.040 --> 00:01:30.950
me.

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:33.950
A lot of

00:01:33.960 --> 00:01:39.510
people are focused on validation

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:43.350
here and what money they can have, what

00:01:43.360 --> 00:01:46.469
big house, what big car, what TV

00:01:46.479 --> 00:01:50.590
program,

00:01:50.600 --> 00:01:55.630
whatever. But when you sit at the feet of

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:59.310
Jesus and you intercede for people that

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:00.350
are broken, and

00:02:00.350 --> 00:02:00.360
you feel

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:04.910
the heart of

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:07.590
God, you go into the rivers like I'm

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:08.630
talking

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:11.190
about and you're by yourself. You

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:13.430
feel like you have friends and they

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:16.550
abandoned you,

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:19.030
and all you have is just your wife and

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:21.430
your kids—and that's all you really need.

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:22.470
Maybe you're

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:24.390
alone or

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:26.470
whatever; then there's

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:30.229
Jesus. In those times of praying

00:02:30.239 --> 00:02:33.229
for people, He comes and brings a person

00:02:33.239 --> 00:02:35.470
to you in the spirit realm, and you

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:37.470
see them, and then you pick them

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:39.910
up and intercede for them and

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:41.309
love on them in the spirit, and they

00:02:41.319 --> 00:02:43.430
don't even know that you're doing it.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:45.190
I'll pass people on the

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:48.910
road and I'll see a spirit of suicide

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:50.949
or whatever on that

00:02:50.959 --> 00:02:53.149
individual, and I'll just break down and

00:02:53.159 --> 00:02:56.470
sob and weep for them and intercede

00:02:56.480 --> 00:02:59.190
for them for hours. I don't even know

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:02.030
that individual;

00:03:02.040 --> 00:03:05.229
all I know is I see

00:03:05.239 --> 00:03:09.030
pain, and the Lord will say, 'You need to

00:03:09.030 --> 00:03:09.040
pray.'When

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:11.869
you get

00:03:11.879 --> 00:03:15.710
compassion for the

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:23.910
lost, you start feeling His heartbeat for

00:03:23.920 --> 00:03:25.710
people;

00:03:25.720 --> 00:03:31.789
it changes you.

00:03:31.799 --> 00:03:34.229
In the last two

00:03:34.239 --> 00:03:39.149
days, He visited me again in the spirit

00:03:39.159 --> 00:03:41.750
and

00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:44.710
He started talking to me. Like I told

00:03:44.720 --> 00:03:47.869
you

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:53.589
all, I weep for

00:03:53.599 --> 00:04:01.229
humanity for Him.

00:04:01.229 --> 00:04:01.239
I

00:04:01.239 --> 00:04:16.110
hope the Holy Spirit can get through

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:22.310
this. You see what's

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:26.550
coming in intercessory prayer;

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.749
He tells you the weight of it. The

00:04:28.749 --> 00:04:28.759
plague

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:31.350
tells you the responsibility of

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:36.029
what's

00:04:36.039 --> 00:04:38.710
coming. Yesterday was a very intense day

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:39.749
for

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:42.310
me.

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:45.070
I was praying

00:04:45.080 --> 00:04:49.830
for

00:04:49.830 --> 00:04:49.840
a

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:53.830
pastor and interceding for some

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:56.469
friends. For two days in a row now, He's

00:04:56.479 --> 00:04:58.710
been downloading stuff for me. I was

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:00.430
driving down the road and I was just

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:01.909
interceding, in deep

00:05:01.919 --> 00:05:03.790
intercession like I do when I'm driving

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:06.950
around, and all of a sudden the Lord

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:09.270
opened my

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:11.830
eyes and He said to me, 'I'm going to

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:14.469
show you some things.'I looked out

00:05:14.479 --> 00:05:16.350
and I was looking at a grocery store,

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:18.230
and I was actually in the grocery

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:21.590
store but He took me to the future and I

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:23.150
saw this massive

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:27.110
tent in the

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:30.150
grocery store parking lot.

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:31.909
There were white

00:05:31.909 --> 00:05:31.919
cots

00:05:31.919 --> 00:05:35.029
all in the parking lot of this

00:05:35.039 --> 00:05:38.469
grocery store. Literally, I would say

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:41.270
there were probably a thousand

00:05:41.270 --> 00:05:41.280
cots,

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:44.629
but they were all military-style

00:05:44.629 --> 00:05:44.639
cots, and

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:48.629
they were white-looking. On

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:50.390
these cots, there

00:05:50.390 --> 00:05:50.400
were

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:53.670
bodies. I saw an IV sitting beside

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:56.590
the body and I saw the person with the

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:58.629
sheet over the top of their

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:02.230
head; all these bodies were in this

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:04.950
grocery store parking lot.

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:07.150
Then He took me to the hospital, and all

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:10.110
the hospitals were completely full.

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:12.909
There was no room, and

00:06:12.919 --> 00:06:16.710
there were military-style camps all

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:19.110
around the

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:23.510
city. Then I saw nurses and

00:06:23.520 --> 00:06:28.550
doctors that were military

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:31.749
trying to take care of these people,

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:33.070
and there was nothing they could do for

00:06:33.080 --> 00:06:34.950
them; they were just comforting them

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:37.350
because they were going to

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:42.430
die. In the spirit, I saw a yellow

00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:46.189
fog that was high around those

00:06:46.199 --> 00:06:48.749
people, and it was

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:52.309
pestilence. It was a

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:54.309
plague, and that was what the Lord was

00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:56.790
showing me—it was

00:06:56.790 --> 00:06:56.800
waist-high and

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:58.510
it was coming out.

00:06:58.510 --> 00:06:58.520
It

00:06:58.520 --> 00:07:02.189
was an airborne

00:07:02.199 --> 00:07:05.830
virus, and I saw it at the

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:08.909
base of them all there.

00:07:08.919 --> 00:07:11.670
Then the Lord took me and I saw a

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:15.469
complete shutdown of society beyond

00:07:15.479 --> 00:07:17.510
anything you can comprehend, even worse

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:21.029
than

00:07:21.039 --> 00:07:26.749
2020. If you thought 2020 was

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:31.629
bad, this makes that look like child's

00:07:31.639 --> 00:07:34.670
play.

00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:37.589
This is on steroids, beyond

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:39.909
anything you can

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:44.710
comprehend. We as a nation, as a

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:48.189
generation, have never seen this before.

00:07:48.199 --> 00:07:51.390
The Lord said what is about

00:07:51.400 --> 00:07:54.869
to happen has not happened for hundreds

00:07:54.879 --> 00:07:59.990
and hundreds of years.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:04.309
He told me it

00:08:04.319 --> 00:08:06.790
would be a type and shadow of the Black

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:11.550
Death in the

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:13.550
1300s. I

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:15.149
saw

00:08:15.159 --> 00:08:18.830
nobody able to do work in factories,

00:08:18.840 --> 00:08:22.790
nobody able to work and make money of

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:25.990
any kind. It was a complete

00:08:25.990 --> 00:08:26.000
shutdown

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:29.909
worldwide. No grocery

00:08:29.919 --> 00:08:32.430
stores were able to be opened; it

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:34.509
was like essentials only,

00:08:34.519 --> 00:08:37.070
but people were

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:38.589
so

00:08:38.599 --> 00:08:41.709
scared of this

00:08:41.719 --> 00:08:43.389
thing

00:08:43.399 --> 00:08:45.870
that there was no movement of

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:47.829
humanity. If you got it, you

00:08:47.839 --> 00:08:52.110
weren't here anymore. There was no antidote for your arm—nothing. There was

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:57.870
nothing to stop it.

00:08:57.880 --> 00:09:00.630
Anybody who contracted this

00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:03.030
thing was

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:08.550
gone. Then I saw 350 million

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:13.990
worldwide, then I saw thirty million over the United

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:16.110
States.

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:19.150
The Lord warned me about the

00:09:19.150 --> 00:09:19.160
terrible

00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:23.829
things that would happen

00:09:23.839 --> 00:09:26.990
here. I was shown

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:34.310
all paper currency was completely

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.110
done away with because people were

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:39.230
afraid to touch it; it was more of a

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:42.430
digital platform. I saw an

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:46.150
implementation even more because of

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:49.870
being afraid to touch

00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:54.870
it. I saw

00:09:54.880 --> 00:10:00.670
mega-churches

00:10:00.680 --> 00:10:03.829
completely shut

00:10:03.839 --> 00:10:08.310
down, a complete melting of a

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:10.030
financial

00:10:10.040 --> 00:10:12.870
structure beyond anybody's comprehension

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:14.550
that we've never seen

00:10:14.560 --> 00:10:19.110
before.

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:23.630
We thought 2020 was bad;

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:25.509
this was far more than anything I

00:10:25.519 --> 00:10:29.790
can tell you. The people passing away,

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:33.190
like I said, had white sheets over them, and

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:37.069
it was very

00:10:37.079 --> 00:10:41.150
heavy. The Lord showed

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:45.550
me a massive hurricane

00:10:45.560 --> 00:10:47.829
again, but it was

00:10:47.839 --> 00:10:51.590
not a real, actual hurricane; it was in

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:55.389
the spirit realm. He said, 'Son,

00:10:55.399 --> 00:10:58.470
the very beginning of the bands are

00:10:58.480 --> 00:11:00.470
just starting to touch.'In the spirit

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:02.430
realm, it was a

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:04.389
massive hurricane, and He said the eye of

00:11:04.399 --> 00:11:07.030
the storm is way out there. From what

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:10.230
you're seeing even as of today, we may be

00:11:10.240 --> 00:11:12.310
thinking it's turbulent times in the

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:14.829
natural with all the stuff we see going

00:11:14.839 --> 00:11:17.629
on in the

00:11:17.629 --> 00:11:17.639
world—with

00:11:17.639 --> 00:11:19.190
rioting

00:11:19.190 --> 00:11:19.200
and

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:21.710
all this

00:11:21.710 --> 00:11:21.720
stuff—but

00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:24.710
it was just the outer bands.

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:27.030
Even through 2020, it was just the

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:29.310
beginning;

00:11:29.320 --> 00:11:31.430
the bands were just coming on the shore of

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.389
the

00:11:33.399 --> 00:11:36.509
world. We hadn't even got to

00:11:36.519 --> 00:11:39.710
the eye of the storm;

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:41.350
it was not even making

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:43.150
landfall yet. The great winds

00:11:43.160 --> 00:11:45.389
weren't even here yet; it was just barely

00:11:45.399 --> 00:11:47.310
the streaks like

00:11:47.320 --> 00:11:51.110
you would see on the radar on

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:55.190
TV. He told me this will be

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:57.710
more than just this in the

00:11:57.720 --> 00:11:59.990
future.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:04.310
I saw stadiums—when the

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:07.550
financial system crashes again, He said

00:12:07.550 --> 00:12:07.560
there

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:09.750
will be a financial crash,

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:11.949
plague,

00:12:11.959 --> 00:12:14.710
economic turmoil

00:12:14.720 --> 00:12:17.870
worldwide, a new digital dollar, a

00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:21.829
new everything.

00:12:21.839 --> 00:12:25.670
Then I was asking

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:29.389
Him—please

00:12:29.399 --> 00:12:31.629
help me, Holy Spirit, I

00:12:31.639 --> 00:12:34.069
don't want to skip around—He showed me,

00:12:34.079 --> 00:12:36.590
like I said, when they have big

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:39.389
football games and baseball, people

00:12:39.399 --> 00:12:41.590
won't even be able to afford to pay to

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:42.910
get into those

00:12:42.920 --> 00:12:44.949
stadiums. They won't

00:12:44.949 --> 00:12:44.959
have

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:46.750
enough finances; those people

00:12:46.760 --> 00:12:50.590
are all

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:52.949
broke. But this is some hope I want to

00:12:52.959 --> 00:12:54.870
tell you:

00:12:54.880 --> 00:12:58.150
after I saw all the cots and all the spirit

00:12:58.150 --> 00:12:58.160
realm

00:12:58.160 --> 00:13:03.269
stuff, I saw people—men and women

00:13:03.279 --> 00:13:07.350
of God—dressed in

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:11.310
white. The men had white

00:13:11.320 --> 00:13:14.310
suits on in the spirit realm with

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.430
white ties, white shirts, white

00:13:16.440 --> 00:13:18.389
slacks, and white

00:13:18.399 --> 00:13:23.269
shoes. Outside of them was a

00:13:23.279 --> 00:13:28.509
glowing look, like honey—the honey

00:13:28.509 --> 00:13:28.519
was

00:13:28.519 --> 00:13:30.829
saturating

00:13:30.829 --> 00:13:30.839
them—and

00:13:30.839 --> 00:13:34.509
there was a light that

00:13:34.519 --> 00:13:38.670
shined outside of them that went about

00:13:38.670 --> 00:13:38.680
three

00:13:38.680 --> 00:13:43.030
feet. The glory of the Lord was so

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:46.110
present on these individuals, and the

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:50.150
Lord said, 'This will be the remnant that

00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:53.350
rises up, and there will be a

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:55.910
supernatural covering over them when

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:59.790
this stuff happens.'I saw a glory

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:03.590
glow all over these remnant people, and

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:06.269
when this plague

00:14:06.279 --> 00:14:09.189
tries to get on them, it

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:11.910
died because of the honey glow.

00:14:11.920 --> 00:14:14.470
The honey glow ate that smog that I told you was waist-high. The smog would try to penetrate the honey glow,

00:14:17.360 --> 00:14:20.949
and

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:27.629
it would kill it.

00:14:27.639 --> 00:14:29.629
The glory of the

00:14:29.629 --> 00:14:29.639
Lord—He

00:14:29.639 --> 00:14:32.870
said this to me: 'For what

00:14:32.880 --> 00:14:34.749
is coming,

00:14:34.759 --> 00:14:38.509
son, you will not survive it if you do

00:14:38.519 --> 00:14:41.430
not have an understanding of the

00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:45.030
power of the name of the revelation

00:14:45.030 --> 00:14:45.040
of Jesus.'He

00:14:45.040 --> 00:14:47.710
said the people who are going

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:51.150
to walk in this honey glow will have

00:14:51.160 --> 00:14:54.790
a revelation of the glory and the power

00:14:54.800 --> 00:14:57.790
of the Lord inside of them

00:14:57.800 --> 00:15:00.230
and a revelation of the

00:15:00.230 --> 00:15:00.240
Covenant—revelation

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:03.389
knowledge, not just

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:05.230
saying it out of your

00:15:05.240 --> 00:15:08.590
mouth. He said it would be a

00:15:08.590 --> 00:15:08.600
rhema

00:15:08.600 --> 00:15:11.550
word. He said, 'If you're waiting until

00:15:11.560 --> 00:15:12.430
this happens—which

00:15:12.430 --> 00:15:12.440
is

00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:15.350
why I'm telling you to tell my

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:17.509
people to get in the Word

00:15:17.509 --> 00:15:17.519
and

00:15:17.519 --> 00:15:20.189
teach my people to

00:15:20.189 --> 00:15:20.199
pray—if

00:15:20.199 --> 00:15:22.990
they wait until this is

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:25.910
coming at their door, it will be

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:28.990
too late.'This is going to be a

