show us what we need to get

00:37:34.720 --> 00:37:37.349
for our families. Give

00:37:37.349 --> 00:37:37.359
us

00:37:37.359 --> 00:37:39.550
wisdom so that we're not moved out of

00:37:39.560 --> 00:37:43.270
