00:38:15.280 --> 00:38:16.829
my

00:38:16.839 --> 00:38:18.150
Advocate, my Comforter, my

00:38:18.150 --> 00:38:18.160
Standby—You

00:38:18.160 --> 00:38:20.230
are

00:38:20.240 --> 00:38:23.710
