00:38:55.079 --> 00:38:59.950
I pray a spirit of peace, for You said,

00:38:59.960 --> 00:39:02.270
'Peace I leave with you; my

00:39:02.280 --> 00:39:04.230
peace I give to

00:39:04.230 --> 00:39:04.240
