00:39:11.150 --> 00:39:11.160
or

00:39:11.160 --> 00:39:13.829
flesh; we're moved by

00:39:13.839 --> 00:39:16.550
the love of God. I thank You, Lord,

00:39:16.560 --> 00:39:19.910
