00:40:00.950 --> 00:40:00.960
I

00:40:00.960 --> 00:40:03.710
thank

00:40:03.710 --> 00:40:03.720
You,

00:40:03.720 --> 00:40:06.510
Lord,

00:40:06.520 --> 00:40:08.829
